add(CompactTrie) - Method in class trie.CompactTrie
This Add function allows the function not to add words, but directly CompactTries (used in the "add" function, to transfer CompactTries from one to another when a new one as to be put between to other) Exemple : Citron -> nier | ADD "Ci" | Ci -> tron -> [nier]) the part of word [nier], had to be moved from the "Citron" CompactTrie to the "tron" one.
